{"tid":1838103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門宣布非高等教育學校延至2月10日或之後上課","createTime":"2020-01-24T01:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T02:18:40.000Z","uid":226984,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"286e6555678d7b68c09ac88a53c655b8b7806acb","tid":1838103,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"澳門教育暨青年局宣布，因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，非高等教育學校在農曆新年假期後，延至2月10日或之後上課。<br />\n<br />\n澳門當局表示，已通知學校妥善安排學生在家學習的相應方案，私立補充教學輔助中心及持續教育機構同時亦應配合，即延至下月10日或之後運作。<br />\n<br />\n當局亦指，會持續密切監察疫情發展，適時作出相應安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504571-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504571-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=2fe64757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504571-20200124.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e96bd7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504571-20200124.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7c42fecbb9b620ea9df27b1285446b76385e37a4","tid":1838103,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"澳門做野有效率好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a30d8b7a9fc8ab57ac085c27843134803706eefe","tid":1838103,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T01:55:54.000Z","msg":"跟住諗下on99政府叫人唔好去武漢<